{"level":"N1","levelName":"N1","levelNameCn":"高级","emoji":"👑","quizzes":[{"id":"n1-q-001","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"grammar","question":"「公務員にある___行為」填入正确的语法表达。","emoji":"📝","options":[{"id":"a","text":"まじき","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"べき","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"はず","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"わけ","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「～にあるまじきN」表示「作为～不该有的N」。是非常正式的表达。","sourceRef":"n1-g-001"},{"id":"n1-q-002","type":"multiple-choice","topic":"vocabulary","question":"「矛盾」的正确读音是？","emoji":"🔊","options":[{"id":"a","text":"むじゅん","isCorrect":true},{"id":"b","text":"むじょん","isCorrect":false},{"id":"c","text":"ほじゅん","isCorrect":false},{"id":"d","text":"もうじゅん","isCorrect":false}],"explanation":"「矛盾」读作「むじゅん」。注意「矛」读「む」不是「ほ」。","sourceRef":"n1-v-002"}]}
